100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;consumer.start();<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;System.out.println(<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: #eedc70; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\">\"消息消费者已启动\"</span>);<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;}<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" />}<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" /></code></pre>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">示例中用 DefaultMQPushConsumer 类来创建一个消息消费者，通生产者一样一个应用一般创建一个 DefaultMQPushConsumer 对象，该对象一般由应用来维护，可以其设置为全局对象或者单例。该类构造函数入参 consumerGroup 是消息消费者组的名字，需要保证该名字的唯一性。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">接下来指定 NameServer 地址和设置消费者应用程序第一次启动时从队列头部开始消费还是队列尾部开始消费。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">接着调用 subscribe 方法给消费者对象订阅指定主题下的消息，该方法第一个参数是主题名，第二个擦书是标签名，示例表示订阅了主题名 topic_example_java 下所有标签的消息。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">最主要的是注册消息监听器才能消费消息，示例中用的是 Consumer Push 的方式，即设置监听器回调的方式消费消息，默认监听回调方法中 List&nbsp;里只有一条消息，可以通过设置参数来批量接收消息。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">最后调用 start 方法初始化，在整个应用生命周期内只需要调用一次 start 方法。</p>\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.6em 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">启动 Name Server</span></h4>\n<pre style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: normal !important; font-size: 14px; color: #a9b7c6; line-height: 18px; border-radius: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; display: block; overflow-x: auto; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; overflow-y: auto !important; background: #282b2e;\">nohup sh bin/mqnamesrv &amp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" />tail -f ~/logs/rocketmqlogs/namesrv.<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: #f82375; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\">log</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" /></code></pre>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">RocketMQ 核心的四大组件中 Name Server 和 Broker 都是由 RocketMQ 安装包提供的，所以要启动这两个应用才能提供消息服务。首先启动 Name Server，先确保你的机器中已经安装了与 RocketMQ 相匹配的 JDK ，并设置了环境变量 JAVA_HOME ，然后在 RocketMQ 的安装目录下执行 bin 目录下的 mqnamesrv ，默认会将该命令的执行情况输出到当前目录的 nohup.out 文件，最后跟踪日志文件查看 Name Server 的实际运行情况。</p>\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.6em 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">启动 Broker</span></h4>\n<pre style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: normal !important; font-size: 14px; color: #a9b7c6; line-height: 18px; border-radius: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; display: block; overflow-x: auto; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; overflow-y: auto !important; background: #282b2e;\">nohup sh bin/mqbroker -n localhost:<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: #ae87fa; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\">9876</span> &amp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" />tail -f ~/logs/rocketmqlogs/broker.<span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: #f82375; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\">log</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: inherit !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; word-break: inherit !important;\" /></code></pre>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">同样也要确保你的机器中已经安装了与 RocketMQ 相匹配的 JDK ，并设置了环境变量 JAVA_HOME ，然后在 RocketMQ 的安装目录下执行 bin 目录下的 mqbroker ，默认会将该命令的执行情况输出到当前目录的 nohup.out 文件，最后跟踪日志文件查看 Broker 的实际运行情况。</p>\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.6em 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">运行 Consumer</span></h4>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">先运行 Consumer 类，这样当生产者发送消息的时候能在消费者后端看到消息记录。配置没问题的话会看到在控制台打印出<code style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 2px 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: inherit; color: #f82375; line-height: inherit; border-radius: 4px; background: #f8f8f8;\">消息消费者已启动</code></p>\n<h4 style=\"margin: 1.6em 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit;\">运行 Producer</span></h4>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">最后运行 Producer 类，在 Consumer 的控制台能看到接收的消息</p>\n<figure style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 2px solid #eeeeee; border-radius: 6px; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; display: block; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\" title=\"img\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JdLkEI9sZfeR4YAh5xFvwhMbgkhdMr7TX83T9Hd4a6QH6dY1T9bqglMrgeYLnAxPOsVIwgsqca4uXvACtqaRcA/640?tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" data-ratio=\"0.5242857142857142\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JdLkEI9sZfeR4YAh5xFvwhMbgkhdMr7TX83T9Hd4a6QH6dY1T9bqglMrgeYLnAxPOsVIwgsqca4uXvACtqaRcA/640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" data-fail=\"0\" />\n<figcaption style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 0.7em; color: #999999; line-height: inherit; text-align: center;\">img</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">消费者接收到消息</p>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 1.6em 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.3em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ef7060; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; padding: 3px 10px 1px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: inherit; color: #ffffff; line-height: inherit; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px; background: #ef7060;\">Spring 整合 RocketMQ</span></h3>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.7em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: #ffffff;\">不同于 RabbitMQ、ActiveMQ、Kafka 等消息中间件，Spring 社区已经通过多种方式提供了对这些中间件产品集成，例如通过 spring-jms 整合 ActiveMQ、通过 Spring AMQP 项目下的 spring-rabbit 整合 RabbitMQ、通过 spring-kafka 整合 kafka ，通过他们可以在 Spring 项目中更方便使用其 API 。目前在 Spring 框架中集成 RocketMQ 有三种方式，一是将消息生产者和消费者定义成 bean 